                                ],
                                "answer": "Windows"
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "File Management",
                    "content": {
                        "explanation": "Files are stored in folders (also called directories). We can create, rename, move, copy, and delete files and folders. Organizing files properly helps us find them easily. Common file types include documents (.doc, .pdf), images (.jpg, .png), and videos (.mp4)."
